<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <meta charset="utf-8">
    <title>Welcome to {{courseName}}</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: #333;
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 20px;
        }
        .header {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #667eea 0%, #764ba2 100%);
            color: white;
            padding: 30px;
            text-align: center;
            border-radius: 10px 10px 0 0;
        }
        .content {
            background: #f9f9f9;
            padding: 30px;
            border-radius: 0 0 10px 10px;
        }
        .button {
            display: inline-block;
            padding: 12px 24px;
            background: #667eea;
            color: white;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 5px;
            margin: 20px 0;
        }
        .footer {
            text-align: center;
            margin-top: 30px;
            color: #666;
            font-size: 14px;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="header">
        <h1>Welcome to {{courseName}}!</h1>
        <p>You're now enrolled and ready to start learning</p>
    </div>
    
    <div class="content">
        <h2>Hello {{studentName}},</h2>
        
        <p>Congratulations! You've successfully enrolled in <strong>{{courseName}}</strong>.</p>
        
        <p>Your course instructor is <strong>{{instructorName}}</strong>, who will guide you through this learning journey.</p>
        
        <h3>What's next?</h3>
        <ul>
            <li>Access your course materials</li>
            <li>Complete modules at your own pace</li>
            <li>Participate in discussions</li>
            <li>Take quizzes to test your knowledge</li>
            <li>Earn your certificate upon completion</li>
        </ul>
        
        <p><strong>Enrollment Date:</strong> {{enrollmentDate}}</p>
        
        <div style="text-align: center;">
            <a href="#" class="button">Start Learning Now</a>
        </div>
        
        <p>If you have any questions, feel free to reach out to your instructor or use the discussion forums.</p>
        
        <p>Happy learning!</p>
        
        <p>Best regards,<br>
        The E-Learning Platform Team</p>
    </div>
    
    <div class="footer">
        <p>This email was sent to you because you enrolled in a course on our platform.</p>
        <p>Â© 2025 E-Learning Platform. All rights reserved.</p>
    </div>
</body>
</html> 